            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Getting their kids an excellent, moral education is every parent's ambition. Without concern for anything else, every child should be building the foundation for a robust educational system. With some of the best education available under the ICSE Board, my child is enrolled in the LKG programme at Mater Die International School. His amount of tutoring is far more than I could have ever expected. The school provides a wonderful environment, and they are effective at communicating with parents about school-related matters and taking care of the health and safety of their pupils. A typical, established institution has first-rate features throughout, including knowledgeable administrative staff. The aforementioned school technique was explained by Mrs. Dayana very clearly when he joined.  Furthermore. Together with the incredibly welcoming and kind academic instructors, the principal, Mrs. Pandiselvi, runs this school in an amazing way and exhibits outstanding leadership in the academic realm. All academic and administrative problems are being handled by Mr. Martin, the correspondent, who will provide the school with good future support. With all of my best wishes, I say \"go ahead.\" I'm very grateful.👏👏👏👏👍",
          "publisher": {
